name: blue lake
about: Blue lake is a small lake, not super busy, you'll find some great hidden spots here!

name: lake minnetonka
about: Lake Minnetonka is fairly large and busy, be sure to get there early to have the best chance.

name: birch lake
about: In Big lake MN, Birch lake is a great place to catch a ton of panfish for an afternoon fish fry

name: red lake
about: In northern MN, red lake has plenty of great fishing holes for catching Bass

name: lake hiro
about: A totally real lake, where you catch fish as soon as you drop your line! You will run out of bait!
